snippet.title: SPEED DREAMS - A Dirt Race at Garguree
snippet.description:
You can find this game and more info about this Open Source project on:
https://www.speed-dreams.net
This time we bring you a bumpy race at Garguree (Australia), using cars from the Rally Series. We will drive an FMC Centre 08 RS1 (based on the Ford Focus WRC 08) and compete against other similar cars from this category. The video was recorded using SSGgraph, the default graphic engine.

Music: "Big Rock" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)

http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
